---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Kontakt \u2014 Subtle Somatics" description="Nimm Kontakt auf f\u00fcr pr\u00e4senzbasiertes Coaching und Spinal Energetics in Wien." lang="de" altLangUrl="/contact">

  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="page-hero-inner">
      <h1>Kontakt aufnehmen</h1>
      <p>Melde dich, um deine angeborenen Ressourcen zu erkunden und deine K\u00f6rper-Geist-Verbindung zu vertiefen.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="contact-grid">
      <div class="contact-form-wrapper">
        <h2>Schreib mir</h2>
        <p>Ich freue mich, von dir zu h\u00f6ren. Ob du Fragen zur Arbeit hast, eine Sitzung buchen m\u00f6chtest oder dich einfach angezogen f\u00fchlst, dich zu verbinden \u2014 schreib mir eine Nachricht.</p>
        <form class="contact-form" action="https://formsubmit.co/connect@subtlesomatics.space" method="POST">
          <input type="hidden" name="_subject" value="Neue Nachricht von subtlesomatics.space" />
          <input type="hidden" name="_captcha" value="false" />
          <input type="hidden" name="_next" value="https://subtlesomatics.space/de/kontakt" />
          <input type="text" name="_honey" style="display:none" />
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="name">Dein Vorname</label>
            <input type="text" id="name" name="name" placeholder="Dein Name" />
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="email">Deine E-Mail-Adresse <span class="required">*</span></label>
            <input type="email" id="email" name="email" placeholder="deine@email.com" required />
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="message">Deine Nachricht <span class="required">*</span></label>
            <textarea id="message" name="message" rows="6" placeholder="Was ist gerade lebendig in dir?" required></textarea>
          </div>
          <button type="submit" class="btn btn-filled">Nachricht senden</button>
        </form>
      </div>
      <div class="contact-info">
        <div class="info-card">
          <h3>Kontakt</h3>
          <p><a href="mailto:connect@subtlesomatics.space">connect@subtlesomatics.space</a></p>
        </div>
        <div class="info-card">
          <h3>Folgen</h3>
          <p><a href="https://www.instagram.com/subtlesomatics/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">@subtlesomatics</a></p>
        </div>
        <div class="info-card">
          <h3>Sitzungen</h3>
          <p>Online (Zoom) und vor Ort</p>
          <p class="info-sub">Wien, \u00d6sterreich</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section-cream">
    <div class="location-content text-center">
      <h2>Wo du mich findest</h2>
      <p>Sitzungen sind online (via Zoom) und vor Ort in Wien, \u00d6sterreich verf\u00fcgbar.</p>
      <p>Ich freue mich auf dich und f\u00fchle mich geehrt, dich begleiten zu d\u00fcrfen \u2014 genau dort, wo du gerade stehst.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  .page-hero { background: var(--color-meteorite-dark); color: var(--color-light); padding: 10rem 2rem 6rem; text-align: center; }
  .page-hero-inner { max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .page-hero h1 { color: var(--color-light); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .page-hero p { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8); font-size: 1.15rem; margin: 0 auto; }

  .contact-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1.5fr 1fr; gap: 4rem; align-items: start; }
  .contact-form-wrapper h2 { margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .contact-form-wrapper > p { margin-bottom: 2rem; color: var(--color-dark); }
  .contact-form { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1.5rem; }
  .form-group { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.5rem; }
  .form-group label { font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.05em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--color-gray); }
  .required { color: var(--color-primary); }
  .form-group input, .form-group textarea {
    font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 1rem; padding: 0.85rem 1rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(47,28,106,0.15); background: var(--color-cream);
    color: var(--color-dark); transition: border-color 0.3s ease; font-weight: 300;
  }
  .form-group input:focus, .form-group textarea:focus { outline: none; border-color: var(--color-primary-light); }
  .form-group textarea { resize: vertical; min-height: 120px; }

  .contact-info { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 2rem; padding-top: 1rem; }
  .info-card h3 { color: var(--color-primary); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-style: italic; font-size: 1.3rem; }
  .info-card p { color: var(--color-dark); font-size: 0.95rem; }
  .info-sub { color: var(--color-gray); font-size: 0.85rem; margin-top: 0.25rem; }

  .location-content { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .location-content h2 { margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .location-content p { margin: 0 auto 1rem; color: var(--color-dark); }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .contact-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 3rem; }
  }
</style>
